      <title>生产者-消费者与阻塞队列</title>
      <link>https://wangy325.top/post/tech/java/concurrency/%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E8%80%85-%E6%B6%88%E8%B4%B9%E8%80%85%E4%B8%8E%E9%98%BB%E5%A1%9E%E9%98%9F%E5%88%97/</link>
